WANTS TO GO THROUGH,

00:14:04.930 --> 00:14:08.060
IT'S, "NO. NO, YOU CAN'T
COME THROUGH HERE."

00:14:08.060 --> 00:14:10.900
SO THE ELECTRONS GO THROUGH
SOME EXTERIOR CIRCUIT,

00:14:10.900 --> 00:14:14.330
AND ON THEIR WAY, WE MAKE THEM
DO SOME WORK FOR US.

00:14:14.330 --> 00:14:16.060
YOU'VE GOT TO TURN ON
MY LIGHT BULB.

00:14:16.060 --> 00:14:17.730
OK? YOU GOT TO
MAKE MY COMPUTER WORK.

00:14:17.730 --> 00:14:19.400
YOU GOT TO MAKE
MY TV WORK.

00:14:19.400 --> 00:14:21.060
YOU GOT TO MAKE
MY STEREO WORK.

00:14:21.060 --> 00:14:23.060
YOU GOT TO TURN ON
THE HEATER.

00:14:23.060 --> 00:14:27.060
NOW THE ELECTRONS GO AROUND,
AND AT THE SAME TIME,

00:14:27.060 --> 00:14:29.830
THE PROTONS ARE MAKING THEIR WAY
ACROSS THE MEMBRANE,

00:14:29.830 --> 00:14:32.660
AND THEN ON THE OTHER SIDE
OF THE MEMBRANE,

00:14:32.660 --> 00:14:35.760
THE ELECTRONS, THE PROTONS,
THE OXYGEN ALL MEET TOGETHER,

00:14:35.760 --> 00:14:39.500
AND WE PRODUCE WATER
AS A BY-PRODUCT.

00:14:40.930 --> 00:14:43.600
IF HYDROGEN IS USED
AS THE FUEL INPUT,

00:14:43.600 --> 00:14:48.360
THEN THE EXHAUST
IS PURE, CLEAN WATER.

00:14:48.360 --> 00:14:50.760
WE WOULD ABSOLUTELY NOT BE
ADDING TO GLOBAL WARMING

00:14:50.760 --> 00:14:53.100
IN THAT SCENARIO.

00:14:54.260 --> 00:14:56.260
IF YOU TAKE A LOOK
AT A FUEL CELL,

00:14:56.260 --> 00:14:57.860
ESSENTIALLY IT ALL
BOILS DOWN TO--

00:14:57.860 --> 00:15:01.430
WHAT IS THIS MEMBRANE
MATERIAL MADE OUT OF, OK?

00:15:01.430 --> 00:15:04.230
WE WERE ACTUALLY
SOSSINA'S FIRST
2 GRAD STUDENTS,

00:15:04.230 --> 00:15:05.960
NUMBER ONE
AND NUMBER TWO.

00:15:05.960 --> 00:15:07.560
