PARTICULAR MATERIALS

00:15:07.560 --> 00:15:11.760
THAT HAVE WHAT ARE CALLED
SUPERPROTONIC PHASE TRANSITIONS.

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:13.230
AND I WAS, LIKE, "WHOA!"

00:15:13.230 --> 00:15:15.000
IT'S A NEW CLASS
OF MATERIALS,

00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:17.860
WHICH HAS NEVER BEEN
INVESTIGATED BEFORE.

00:15:17.860 --> 00:15:19.300
IT'S SUPERPROTONIC.

