AND THEN, YOU KNOW,
WE REALLY WORKED ON

00:15:25.730 --> 00:15:27.930
UNDERSTANDING
THE THERMODYNAMICS

00:15:27.930 --> 00:15:32.030
THAT MAKE THESE MATERIALS
DO WHAT THEY DO.

