AND WE ACTUALLY TOOK
THE MATERIALS,

00:15:33.860 --> 00:15:35.930
SMASHED THEM TOGETHER TO MAKE
THIS SPECIAL MEMBRANE,

00:15:35.930 --> 00:15:39.130
AND CREATED ELECTRICITY
FROM HYDROGEN.

00:15:39.130 --> 00:15:41.460
AND RIGHT NOW, WE'RE
DEFINITELY DOING THIS

