IN A CRUDE MANNER,

00:15:42.730 --> 00:15:45.230
BUT THIS IS ONE OF THE
THINGS THAT WE HAVE TO DO

00:15:45.230 --> 00:15:47.030
TO BASICALLY MAKE THIS

00:15:47.030 --> 00:15:49.360
A HIGHLY REFINED
COMMERCIAL PROCESS.

00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:53.100
SO YOU'RE BASICALLY
MAKING A SANDWICH--

00:15:53.100 --> 00:15:55.300
MEMBRANE, AND THEN WE HAVE
HYDROGEN ELECTRODE

