HOW OLD THEY'RE GOING TO BE

00:27:54.260 --> 00:27:57.660
WHEN YOU DIE.

00:27:57.660 --> 00:27:59.260
I MEAN, MARK CAME HOME,

00:27:59.260 --> 00:28:02.500
IMMEDIATELY CANCELED EVERYTHING
THAT HE HAD ON HIS DOCKET.

00:28:02.500 --> 00:28:05.330
Mark: YOU GO FROM BEING
SOMEONE WHO'S A CONTROL--

00:28:05.330 --> 00:28:07.800
WE'RE ALL CONTROL FREAKS;

00:28:07.800 --> 00:28:10.060
BELIEVE ME, EVERY FACULTY MEMBER
IS A CONTROL FREAK--

00:28:10.060 --> 00:28:14.730
TO ACTUALLY HAVING EVERYTHING
TAKEN OUT OF YOUR CONTROL.

00:28:14.730 --> 00:28:18.060
YOU KNOW, YOUR NICE
COMFORTABLE LIFE

00:28:18.060 --> 00:28:20.560
GETS, YOU KNOW,
ALL OF A SUDDEN DESTROYED.

00:28:20.560 --> 00:28:23.730
Mary: WITHIN A 2-WEEK PERIOD,

00:28:23.730 --> 00:28:25.730
I HAD GONE THROUGH
ALL KINDS OF TESTS

00:28:25.730 --> 00:28:28.660
AND HAD A MASTECTOMY.

00:28:28.660 --> 00:28:30.800
AND THEN THE THIRD
DOCTOR I SAW

00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:32.830
JUST RECOMMENDED A REALLY,
REALLY AGGRESSIVE

00:28:32.830 --> 00:28:35.230
FORM OF CHEMOTHERAPY.

00:28:36.760 --> 00:28:40.500
I HAD A DRUG
CALLED ADRIAMYCIN,

00:28:40.500 --> 00:28:42.860
AND IT'S NICKNAMED
"THE RED DEATH."

00:28:42.860 --> 00:28:46.000
AND THAT'S WHAT
IT REALLY FELT LIKE.

00:28:47.930 --> 00:28:51.730
I WOULD LAY IN BED AND THROW UP
CONTINUOUSLY FOR 2 DAYS,

00:28:51.730 --> 00:28:55.530
NOT EAT, HAIR LOSS.

00:28:55.530 --> 00:28:59.930
YOU'RE MORE SUSCEPTIBLE
TO INFECTION.

00:28:59.930 --> 00:29:03.400
I MEAN, YOU JUST GET SO WEAK.

00:29:03.400 --> 00:29:07.460
Mark: YOUR FOCUS TURNS INTO
BATTLING THE TREATMENT.

00:29:07.460 --> 00:29:11.230
WHAT YOU'RE TRYING TO DO
IS SURVIVE THE TREATMENTS.

00:29:11.230 --> 00:29:14.900
Mary: IT'S REALLY HARD TO GO
INTO A DOCTOR'S OFFICE

00:29:14.900 --> 00:29:16.900
AND TO PUT SOMETHING
IN YOUR VEINS

00:29:16.900 --> 00:29:19.930
THAT YOU KNOW IS
GOING TO MAKE YOU SICK.

00:29:19.930 --> 00:29:22.400
YEAH, THINKING
ABOUT IT NOW,

00:29:22.400 --> 00:29:25.460
JUST, YOU KNOW, BRINGING UP
THESE MEMORIES, I...

00:29:29.100 --> 00:29:31.830
YOU LIKE TO THINK THERE'S
A REASON FOR EVERYTHING,

00:29:31.830 --> 00:29:33.760
AND SOMETIMES
I LIKE TO THINK

00:29:33.760 --> 00:29:37.000
THAT THERE'S A REASON
THAT I GOT SICK.

00:29:37.000 --> 00:29:40.000
WHEN I WAS LITERALLY
THROWING UP EVERY DAY,

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:43.000
ALMOST EVERY HOUR
FOR A WHOLE MONTH.

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:44.730
I WOULD TURN
TO HIM AND SAY,

00:29:44.730 --> 00:29:46.530
"MARK, THERE'S GOT TO BE
A BETTER WAY.

00:29:46.530 --> 00:29:49.430
"YOU KNOW, YOU'VE
GOT TO FIND OUT

00:29:49.430 --> 00:29:51.500
"HOW TO HAVE THE TREATMENT,
GET RID OF THE CANCER,

00:29:51.500 --> 00:29:53.960
BUT NOT GO THROUGH
ALL THESE SIDE EFFECTS."

00:29:53.960 --> 00:29:57.200
Mark: WHEN SHE SAID,
"THERE HAS TO BE A BETTER WAY,"

00:29:57.200 --> 00:30:00.100
THAT WAS REALLY
THE TURNING POINT.

00:30:00.100 --> 00:30:03.900
CANCER--WHAT DID
I KNOW ABOUT IT?

00:30:03.900 --> 00:30:06.330
IT WAS WAY OUT
OF MY COMFORT ZONE

00:30:06.330 --> 00:30:08.830
FROM A SCIENTIFIC
POINT OF VIEW.

00:30:08.830 --> 00:30:13.100
MARY SAID, "WELL, WHAT KIND
OF EXCUSE IS THAT?

00:30:13.100 --> 00:30:15.160
"YOU PEOPLE OVER AT CALTECH
ARE SMART.

00:30:15.160 --> 00:30:17.000
"YOU GUYS
HAVE A HISTORY

00:30:17.000 --> 00:30:18.760
"OF BEING ABLE TO SOLVE
SIGNIFICANT PROBLEMS.

00:30:18.760 --> 00:30:22.000
YOU KNOW, WHY DON'T YOU
WORK ON IT?"

00:30:22.000 --> 00:30:24.730
EASIER SAID THAN DONE.

00:30:34.100 --> 00:30:37.660
Ray: CANCER IS NO JOKE,

00:30:37.660 --> 00:30:40.430
BUT TREATMENT IS WORSE.

00:30:40.430 --> 00:30:42.330
AT THE BEGINNING
OF THE CANCER,

00:30:42.330 --> 00:30:44.300
I TOOK ABOUT
3 MONTHS CHEMO.

00:30:44.300 --> 00:30:48.330
MORE OR LESS, YOU'RE WALKING
LIKE A LIVING ZOMBIE.

00:30:48.330 --> 00:30:51.030
IT WAS HELL ON EARTH FOR ME.

00:30:51.030 --> 00:30:52.760
CHEMO WASN'T WORKING.

00:30:52.760 --> 00:30:55.600
MY CELLS WAS DOUBLING.

00:30:55.600 --> 00:30:58.360
MY CANCER WAS
SPREADING SO FAST.

00:30:58.360 --> 00:31:02.000
I'M IN ONE DAY FOR CHEMO,
SO I ASKED THE ONCOLOGIST,

00:31:02.000 --> 00:31:06.060
"WHY AM I GOING THROUGH THIS
WHEN IT'S NOT WORKING?"

00:31:06.060 --> 00:31:10.630
WELL, THEY FOUND IT HARD
TO BREAK IT TO ME, BUT I KNEW.

00:31:10.630 --> 00:31:12.560
THEY TOLD ME
2 TO 6 MONTHS.

00:31:12.560 --> 00:31:14.160
THE WAY I WAS FEELING,

00:31:14.160 --> 00:31:18.230
I KNEW THAT I WOULDN'T EVEN
LAST 6 MONTHS.

00:31:18.230 --> 00:31:20.900
AND I JUST WENT HOME
WITH MY WIFE,

00:31:20.900 --> 00:31:23.230
AND I THOUGHT ABOUT SPENDING
A COUPLE OF MONTHS,

00:31:23.230 --> 00:31:25.630
WHAT I HAVE
WITH MY WIFE.

00:31:25.630 --> 00:31:28.700
AND I WAS MORE CONCERNED
ABOUT HER WELL-BEING,

00:31:28.700 --> 00:31:30.160
MY MOTHER'S WELL-BEING.

00:31:30.160 --> 00:31:33.000
I CALLED MY CHILDREN FROM
NEW ZEALAND, FROM AUSTRALIA.

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:35.630
EVERYBODY CAME THAT TIME.

00:31:35.630 --> 00:31:37.960
SO IT WAS TIME TO ORGANIZE
EVERYTHING FOR THEM

00:31:37.960 --> 00:31:41.000
SO THAT THEY DON'T SUFFER
AFTER I'M GONE.

00:31:42.760 --> 00:31:44.760
ABOUT 2 MONTHS,
2 1/2 MONTHS PASS,

00:31:44.760 --> 00:31:46.500
AND MY ONCOLOGIST
CALLED ME.

00:31:46.500 --> 00:31:49.660
HE ASKED ME IF I WANTED
TO JOIN A STUDY.

00:31:49.660 --> 00:31:51.860
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,
I WASN'T HOPEFUL

00:31:51.860 --> 00:31:53.660
THAT IT'S GOING TO HELP ME.

00:31:53.660 --> 00:31:55.930
BUT AT LEAST IT WILL
HELP SOMEBODY ELSE.

00:31:55.930 --> 00:31:57.260
AND YOUR LAST NAME?

00:31:57.260 --> 00:31:58.660
NATHA. N-A-T-H-A.

00:31:58.660 --> 00:32:00.760
OK. AND DO YOU HAVE
AN ARM BAND ON?

00:32:00.760 --> 00:32:02.400
NO, I HAVEN'T.

00:32:02.400 --> 00:32:04.200
OK. LET ME
GET YOU ONE.

00:32:06.000 --> 00:32:07.830
OK. HAVE A SEAT,
AND I'LL LET THEM

00:32:07.830 --> 00:32:09.700
KNOW YOU'RE HERE, OK?
THANK YOU.

00:32:28.760 --> 00:32:30.660
HA HA HA!

00:32:30.660 --> 00:32:35.430
NOW, WHEN I GOT TO HOSPITAL,
VERY FIRST TREATMENT,

00:32:35.430 --> 00:32:37.760
THEY'RE LOCKING EVERYBODY ELSE
IN A SMALL ROOM--

00:32:37.760 --> 00:32:39.260
NURSES, DOCTORS,
EVERYBODY CHECKING.

00:32:39.260 --> 00:32:42.100
I WAS SECOND, AND THEY WERE
TAKING BLOOD, WHAT,

00:32:42.100 --> 00:32:43.900
EVERY HALF AN HOUR?

00:32:43.900 --> 00:32:46.230
ONLY IN TIME I LEARNED,

00:32:46.230 --> 00:32:48.260
"YOU ARE THE FIRST ONE."

00:32:48.260 --> 00:32:51.800
BY THEN I WAS ALREADY
UNDER THE TREATMENT.

00:32:51.800 --> 00:32:53.760
I KNEW
THAT IT WAS A STUDY,

00:32:53.760 --> 00:32:55.900
BUT I THOUGHT SOMEBODY
MUST BE BEFORE ME.

00:32:55.900 --> 00:32:59.160
IT WAS A HAIR-RAISING MOMENT.

00:32:59.160 --> 00:33:01.000
IF THE MEDICATION
OR SOMETHING GOES WRONG,

00:33:01.000 --> 00:33:02.360
I FORGOT TO SAY GOOD-BYE
TO MY WIFE.

00:33:02.360 --> 00:33:04.400
IF THEY'D TOLD ME,
I WOULD HAVE DONE IT,

00:33:04.400 --> 00:33:06.230
PUT MY LIVING TRUST PROPERLY,

00:33:06.230 --> 00:33:10.460
CALL MY CHILDREN
THE NIGHT BEFORE, AND THEN GO.

00:33:14.400 --> 00:33:17.630
Man: THIS TRIAL IS
REALLY ABOUT SEEING

00:33:17.630 --> 00:33:21.400
WHAT IS IT LIKE TO INJECT
A NANOPARTICLE-CONTAINING DRUG

00:33:21.400 --> 00:33:23.260
INTO A HUMAN.

00:33:25.060 --> 00:33:29.000
Mary: DR. FORMAN WAS MY DOCTOR
AT THE CITY OF HOPE.

00:33:29.000 --> 00:33:31.260
MARK JUST STARTED
TALKING TO HIM,

00:33:31.260 --> 00:33:34.160
AND THAT'S HOW
IT ALL STARTED.

00:33:34.160 --> 00:33:36.760
Forman: WHILE MARY WAS HERE
AT CITY OF HOPE

00:33:36.760 --> 00:33:38.800
UNDERGOING
A REALLY PROLONGED

00:33:38.800 --> 00:33:40.760
AND INTENSIVE
AND HARSH TREATMENT,

00:33:40.760 --> 00:33:43.230
MARK WOULD GO
TO THE LIBRARY

00:33:43.230 --> 00:33:46.100
UNBEKNOWNST TO ANY OF US
AND BEGAN TO STUDY

00:33:46.100 --> 00:33:49.600
WHAT WE KNEW,
NAMELY ABOUT CANCER.

00:33:49.600 --> 00:33:51.800
Mark: THE THING
IN BIOLOGY AND MEDICINE,

00:33:51.800 --> 00:33:53.330
THE LITERATURE
IS ENORMOUS.

00:33:53.330 --> 00:33:56.560
IT'S LIKE THE NIAGARA FALLS.
IF YOU WANTED TO TRY

00:33:56.560 --> 00:33:59.260
TO GET A DRINK AND YOU WERE
UNDERNEATH NIAGARA FALLS,

00:33:59.260 --> 00:34:00.830
HOW WOULD YOU DO THAT?

00:34:00.830 --> 00:34:02.600
BECAUSE IT WOULD JUST,
YOU KNOW, FLOOD YOU TO DEATH.

00:34:02.600 --> 00:34:05.060
Forman: WHAT HE WAS REALLY AFTER
WAS TO SEE

00:34:05.060 --> 00:34:09.560
WHETHER WHAT HE WAS EXPERT AT
COULD BE USED TO DEVELOP

00:34:09.560 --> 00:34:13.300
A BETTER APPROACH
TO TREATING CANCER.

00:34:13.300 --> 00:34:16.060
THERE WAS A POINT AT WHICH
HE ANNOUNCED HIS INTENTIONS

00:34:16.060 --> 00:34:18.430
IN A VERY QUIET,
UNDERSTATED WAY.

00:34:19.530 --> 00:34:22.230
Mark: STEVE CAME OVER
TO MY OFFICE AT CALTECH,

00:34:22.230 --> 00:34:25.960
AND WE WENT ON THE WHITEBOARD
AND STARTED WORKING ON THINGS.

00:34:27.230 --> 00:34:29.160
Forman: I REMEMBER
VERY DISTINCTLY

00:34:29.160 --> 00:34:33.660
HIS DRAWING ON THE BOARD--
THE NANOPARTICLE.

00:34:33.660 --> 00:34:36.430
I KNEW I HAD TO FIGURE OUT
HOW TO MAKE A DRUG

00:34:36.430 --> 00:34:38.100
DO 2 MAJOR THINGS--

00:34:38.100 --> 00:34:40.930
FIRST, IT HAD TO BE EFFECTIVE
AGAINST THE CANCER,

00:34:40.930 --> 00:34:44.700
AND SECOND, IT HAD TO HAVE
MINIMAL SIDE EFFECTS.

00:34:44.700 --> 00:34:46.760
THE MAIN REASON
CONVENTIONAL CHEMO DRUGS,

00:34:46.760 --> 00:34:48.430
LIKE THE ONE MARY TOOK,

00:34:48.430 --> 00:34:50.700
CAUSE SO MANY OF THESE
AWFUL SIDE EFFECTS

00:34:50.700 --> 00:34:53.300
IS BECAUSE THEY'RE MADE UP
OF TINY MOLECULES,

00:34:53.300 --> 00:34:56.430
SO TINY THAT THEY TRAVEL
THROUGH YOUR BLOODSTREAM,

00:34:56.430 --> 00:34:58.430
AND THEY LEAK OUT
OF YOUR BLOOD VESSELS

00:34:58.430 --> 00:35:00.730
TO GO ALL OVER
YOUR BODY.

00:35:00.730 --> 00:35:04.060
SO THE STUFF YOU'RE TAKING
TO KILL THE CANCER CELLS

00:35:04.060 --> 00:35:06.800
ALSO THEN CAN KILL
HEALTHY CELLS.

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:09.560
BUT NANOPARTICLES ARE HUGE.

00:35:09.560 --> 00:35:12.060
COMPARE THAT TO, SAY,
A MOLECULE

00:35:12.060 --> 00:35:13.630
OF A CONVENTIONAL CHEMO DRUG,

00:35:13.630 --> 00:35:15.800
YOU CAN REALLY
SEE THE DIFFERENCE.

00:35:15.800 --> 00:35:19.730
IT-101, SINCE IT'S
A NANOPARTICLE,

00:35:19.730 --> 00:35:22.900
IS TOO BIG TO LEAK OUT
OF NORMAL BLOOD VESSELS

00:35:22.900 --> 00:35:25.230
AND GO INTO
THESE HEALTHY TISSUES.

00:35:25.230 --> 00:35:27.560
AND SO HOPEFULLY
THAT WILL HELP ALLEVIATE

00:35:27.560 --> 00:35:31.100
SOME OF THESE
SIDE EFFECTS.

00:35:31.100 --> 00:35:35.230
THE THING IS, TUMORS DON'T HAVE
NORMAL BLOOD VESSELS.

00:35:35.230 --> 00:35:38.760
WHEN TUMORS GET BIGGER
THAN A FEW MILLIMETERS,

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:41.430
WHICH IS ABOUT THE THICKNESS
OF A CREDIT CARD,

00:35:41.430 --> 00:35:43.330
NOW THEY NEED
NEW BLOOD VESSELS

00:35:43.330 --> 00:35:46.730
TO BE ABLE TO CONTINUE TO GROW
AND GET MORE NUTRIENTS.

00:35:46.730 --> 00:35:49.330
THEY'RE SMART, AND THEY
SEND OUT SIGNALS SAYING,

00:35:49.330 --> 00:35:50.760
"GROW ME SOME NEW
BLOOD VESSELS.

00:35:50.760 --> 00:35:52.330
"BRING ME SOME MORE FOOD

00:35:52.330 --> 00:35:54.760
SO I CAN CONTINUE
TO GROW AND GROW."

00:35:54.760 --> 00:35:57.700
SO THESE NEW BLOOD VESSELS
ARE STRANGE.

00:35:57.700 --> 00:36:01.500
THEY ARE CHAOTIC. THEY'RE NOT
LIKE OUR NORMAL BLOOD VESSELS,

00:36:01.500 --> 00:36:04.060
AND THEY HAVE
BIG HOLES IN THEM

00:36:04.060 --> 00:36:08.230
THAT ALLOW THINGS LIKE IT-101
TO ESCAPE OUT OF THEM.

00:36:08.230 --> 00:36:13.500
OUR EXPECTATION IS, ONCE IT-101
GETS INSIDE OF A CANCER CELL,

00:36:13.500 --> 00:36:14.860
IT'S A DONE DEAL.

00:36:14.860 --> 00:36:18.230
IT'S ALL OVER
FOR THE CANCER CELL.

00:36:18.230 --> 00:36:20.800
Forman: I WAS CONVINCED.

00:36:20.800 --> 00:36:22.600
YOU KNOW, WHAT HE THOUGHT OF,
WHAT HE DREW ON THE BOARD,

00:36:22.600 --> 00:36:24.130
THERE'S SOMETHING HERE,
AND WE'VE GOT TO DO IT,

00:36:24.130 --> 00:36:25.860
WE'VE GOT TO FIND OUT.

