Ray: SO I DID CHECK IN.
ARE MY FOLDERS HERE?

00:36:30.430 --> 00:36:32.730
MY DREAM IS TO TRAVEL.

00:36:32.730 --> 00:36:36.530
IT'S THE BIGGEST DREAM--

00:36:36.530 --> 00:36:38.600
TO TRAVEL
THE TRANS-ALASKAN HIGHWAY,

00:36:38.600 --> 00:36:41.360
TO GO TO ALASKA,
ANCHORAGE, ALASKA.

00:36:41.360 --> 00:36:44.530
I WAS JUST PREPARING FOR THAT,
AND THE CANCER CAME,

00:36:44.530 --> 00:36:46.530
AND I COULDN'T DO IT.

00:36:46.530 --> 00:36:48.660
SO I'M WAITING FOR NOW,

00:36:48.660 --> 00:36:53.500
HOPING THAT IF THIS WORKS,
THIS IS MY DREAM.

