Mark: AS THE 2-MONTH MARK
WAS APPROACHING,

00:37:08.560 --> 00:37:10.730
RAY WAS GOING TO GO IN
FOR HIS SCANS.

00:37:10.730 --> 00:37:12.330
I REALLY WANTED TO SEE
THE RESULTS.

