THE MACHINE'S
GOING TO BE TELLING YOU

00:37:13.900 --> 00:37:15.730
TO TAKE A DEEP BREATH IN
AND HOLD IT.

00:37:15.730 --> 00:37:18.030
AND EVERYONE WAS TELLING ME
TO STAY CALM, STAY CALM,

00:37:18.030 --> 00:37:20.300
THAT YOU WOULDN'T EXPECT
TO SEE SOMETHING

00:37:20.300 --> 00:37:22.430
THIS EARLY
IN A CLINICAL TRIAL.

00:37:22.430 --> 00:37:26.330
YOU KNOW, THE FIRST IN HUMAN,
FIRST PATIENT, LOWEST DOSE,

00:37:26.330 --> 00:37:29.830
BUT I WANTED TO SEE IT
REAL BAD.

00:37:29.830 --> 00:37:31.330
YEAH.
GOOD.

