NO. NO PAIN,
NOTHING.

00:37:34.600 --> 00:37:36.030
FEELING
VERY NICE.

00:37:36.030 --> 00:37:39.600
THE GOOD NEWS WAS
WE WEREN'T SEEING SIDE EFFECTS.

