BUT IN THE BACK
OF MY MIND,

00:37:41.530 --> 00:37:43.200
I'M REALLY WORRIED
THAT, GREAT,

00:37:43.200 --> 00:37:45.700
MAYBE WE HAVE SOMETHING
THAT DOESN'T HAVE SIDE EFFECTS,

00:37:45.700 --> 00:37:48.260
BUT IT ALSO DOESN'T DO
ANYTHING TO THE TUMOR.

00:37:48.260 --> 00:37:49.700
EXCELLENT.

