00:41:37.100 --> 00:41:39.000
WE DIDN'T HAVE
THE RIGHT LAB.

00:41:39.000 --> 00:41:41.430
WE DIDN'T HAVE
THE RIGHT BACKGROUND.

00:41:41.430 --> 00:41:43.930
BUT IT WAS LIKE,
JUST WITH, LIKE, TRACK

00:41:43.930 --> 00:41:45.930
AND WITH GOING INTO
CHEMICAL ENGINEERING,

00:41:45.930 --> 00:41:48.760
IT WAS ANOTHER
BIG CHALLENGE.

00:41:48.760 --> 00:41:53.260
WITH IT-101, THE ENGINEERING
PART OF THE PROBLEM

00:41:53.260 --> 00:41:56.100
WAS TO COMBINE
A POTENT CANCER DRUG

00:41:56.100 --> 00:42:02.260
WITH MATERIALS THAT GET IT
RIGHT INTO CANCER CELLS.

00:42:02.260 --> 00:42:04.530
WE WANTED TO BUILD SOMETHING
LIKE A CUSTOM HOTROD.

00:42:04.530 --> 00:42:06.900
THERE WERE PARTS
THAT PEOPLE KNEW OF,

00:42:06.900 --> 00:42:09.060
BUT WE PUT THEM
TOGETHER IN A WAY

00:42:09.060 --> 00:42:12.230
THAT NO ONE WAS ABLE
TO DO IN THE PAST.

00:42:12.230 --> 00:42:15.500
THE BASIC BUILDING BLOCK
OF IT-101 IS A SUGAR.

00:42:15.500 --> 00:42:17.400
IT'S CALLED CYCLODEXTRIN,

00:42:17.400 --> 00:42:20.330
AND IT WAS FIRST
DISCOVERED IN 1891.

00:42:20.330 --> 00:42:23.230
IT'S NOW USED TO MAKE
LOW-CHOLESTEROL FOODS

00:42:23.230 --> 00:42:26.400
AND TO MAKE HOUSEHOLD PRODUCTS,
LIKE ODOR NEUTRALIZERS.

00:42:26.400 --> 00:42:30.130
BUT A SUGAR POLYMER
IS NOT GOING TO KILL A TUMOR.

00:42:30.130 --> 00:42:33.500
THE CANCER-KILLING POWER
COMES FROM A PLANT EXTRACT

00:42:33.500 --> 00:42:36.030
PRODUCED FROM
THE CAMPTOTHECA TREE,

00:42:36.030 --> 00:42:39.660
WHICH GROWS MAINLY
IN CHINA AND TIBET.

00:42:39.660 --> 00:42:41.430
ITS MEDICINAL PROPERTIES
HAVE BEEN KNOWN

00:42:41.430 --> 00:42:43.630
FOR HUNDREDS OF YEARS
TO TREAT THINGS

00:42:43.630 --> 00:42:46.260
LIKE PSORIASIS, COLDS,
AND STOMACH AILMENTS.

00:42:46.260 --> 00:42:48.100
CAMPTOTHECA LEAVES
PRODUCE A MOLECULE

00:42:48.100 --> 00:42:50.500
CALLED CAMPTOTHECIN.

00:42:50.500 --> 00:42:52.100
IT'S EXTREMELY EFFECTIVE

00:42:52.100 --> 00:42:54.560
AGAINST A LOT OF DIFFERENT
TYPES OF CANCERS.

00:42:54.560 --> 00:42:58.030
BUT IT'S ALSO
EXTREMELY TOXIC.

00:42:58.030 --> 00:43:01.000
SO CAMPTOTHECIN CAN'T BE
USED IN HUMANS

00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:05.160
UNLESS YOU FIGURE OUT A WAY
TO KEEP IT FROM BEING SO TOXIC

00:43:05.160 --> 00:43:07.900
UNTIL IT GETS
INTO THE TUMOR,

00:43:07.900 --> 00:43:10.730
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN YOU ATTACH IT

00:43:10.730 --> 00:43:12.900
TO THE CYCLODEXTRIN POLYMER.

00:43:12.900 --> 00:43:15.730
WHEN WE PUT IT IN WATER,
THESE POLYMER STRANDS

00:43:15.730 --> 00:43:20.300
ZIP TOGETHER AND BECOME
THE IT-101 NANOPARTICLE.

00:43:21.730 --> 00:43:24.900
THE CAMPTOTHECIN IS
CHEMICALLY TRANSFORMED,

00:43:24.900 --> 00:43:27.730
MAKING IT WAY LESS TOXIC.

00:43:27.730 --> 00:43:29.560
IF IT WORKS,
THE WHOLE THING

00:43:29.560 --> 00:43:31.600
IS GOING TO BE
LIKE A TROJAN HORSE.

00:43:31.600 --> 00:43:35.600
LOOKS LIKE A SUGAR, BUT INSIDE
IT'S A LETHAL WEAPON.

00:43:35.600 --> 00:43:38.430
