TO FIGURE OUT A WAY

00:43:47.430 --> 00:43:49.360
TO PUT THOSE TWO THINGS
TOGETHER IN A WAY

00:43:49.360 --> 00:43:52.330
THAT NOBODY HAD THOUGHT
TO DO BEFORE.

